-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4977cb78-fe63-49bb-e916-c36501238600/public\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"320\" data-backh=\"192\" data-imgfileid=\"503492593\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/53129be5-f241-4b9e-8cda-60757998f40a/640.gif\" data-order=\"7\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sparse VideoGen</sup></span></p>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><img data-backh=\"192\" data-backw=\"320\" data-imgfileid=\"503492595\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e7f1d226-a33d-4169-2045-338ff133fb00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ac9ca367-aeb2-4f4d-9c27-116215c04aca/640.gif\" data-order=\"8\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DraftAttention</sup></span></p>\n  <p><strong>Prompt</strong>: \"Realistic, High-quality. A woman is drinking coffee at a café.\"</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-backh=\"512\" data-backw=\"512\" data-imgfileid=\"503492596\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6cc7e70-10f4-48e9-b6e4-3f7325da4800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"512\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c5fcc801-3cbe-4f7c-ac62-673075564119/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; input image</sup>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/41d01832-c9ec-4eb4-6981-9d587cc51500/public\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"320\" data-backh=\"192\" data-imgfileid=\"503492597\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8d618aa7-8c65-480c-81b9-7f174f295150/640.gif\" data-order=\"9\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dense</sup></span></p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-backh=\"192\" data-backw=\"320\" data-imgfileid=\"503492598\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/579df430-2904-46bc-a505-4bb53f109000/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/eaa0cdd6-67a3-45a3-9e6b-8c8481db1ded/640.gif\" data-order=\"10\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DraftAttention</sup></span></p>\n  <p><strong>总结与展望</strong></p>\n  <p>DraftAttention 提供了一种简洁而高效的解决方案：通过低分辨率草图引导、结构化稀疏掩码生成与硬件友好的 token 重排，不仅显著提升了视频扩散模型的推理效率，还在<strong>高稀疏率下保持了出色的生成质量。其「无需训练、即插即用、动态可调、适配主流模型与硬件」的特性</strong>，使其具备良好的工程可落地性和研究拓展性。</p>\n  <p>未来，作者计划进一步结合<strong>量化与蒸馏等技术</strong>，继续优化长视频生成过程中的效率瓶颈，推动高质量视频生成模型走向移动端、边缘端等资源受限场景。</p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "提出无需训练的 DraftAttention 方法，通过动态稀疏注意力机制和低分辨率草图引导，实现视频扩散模型 2 倍 GPU 端到端加速",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "提出无需训练的 DraftAttention 方法，通过动态稀疏注意力机制和低分辨率草图引导，实现视频扩散模型 2 倍 GPU 端到端加速",
  "summary": "文章介绍了美国东北大学和香港中文大学团队提出的 DraftAttention 方法，这是一种针对视频扩散模型的高效加速方案。该方法通过动态稀疏注意力机制，利用低分辨率草图注意力图高效估计 token 重要性并指导高分辨率计算的稀疏模式选择，实现了无需训练、即插即用的 2 倍 GPU 端到端加速。文章详细阐述了方法原理、理论证明（包括近似误差和稀疏掩码误差的可控性）和在 HunyuanVideo 等模型上的实验结果，展示了在高稀疏率下保持视频生成质量的同时显著提升推理速度的优势，性能优于 Sparse VideoGen 等现有方法。",
